    <item>
      <title>保守党撤回对英国选举博彩调查候选人的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/uk-tories-pull-support-from-candidates-caught-in-betting-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克（Rishi Sunak）领导的执政党保守党撤回了对两名候选人的支持，这两名候选人因在首相宣布举行英国大选之前对大选时间的押注而卷入了一项调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/uk-tories-pull-support-from-candidates-caught-in-betting-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:57:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举恐慌开始消退，法国股市回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/french-bonds-hint-investor-nerves-are-calming-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国债券利差从十多年来的最高水平回落，表明投资者对周日提前举行的议会选举可能带来的混乱变得更加乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/french-bonds-hint-investor-nerves-are-calming-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:52:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列法院下令宗教征兵，对内塔尼亚胡造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/top-israel-court-orders-government-to-conscript-religious-men</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列最高法院命令总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡的政府开始征召极端正统派男子服兵役，并停止资助逃避征兵的神学院，这一具有里程碑意义的裁决可能引发政治危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/top-israel-court-orders-government-to-conscript-religious-men</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 08:32:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维基解密创始人朱利安·阿桑奇将认罪，结束美国多年的斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/wikileaks-assange-to-plead-guilty-ending-yearslong-us-battle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据与司法部达成的协议，维基解密联合创始人朱利安·阿桑奇将承认泄露美国国家安全机密，并返回祖国澳大利亚，结束长达近 15 年的起诉之战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/wikileaks-assange-to-plead-guilty-ending-yearslong-us-battle</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 23:16:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
